# Description: Route exit-node prefixes (bits <= 1) to table 53 on UBNT, keeping subnet routes in table 52.
#              Duplicate throw routes into both tables to prevent LAN/WAN breakage with exit nodes.
--- a/wgengine/router/osrouter/router_linux.go	2026-03-13 06:50:01.758937518 +0000
+++ b/wgengine/router/osrouter/router_linux.go	2026-03-13 06:50:28.506816691 +0000
